Feature: Write Xray feature files

    As Xray Connector,
    I want to save feature files downloaded from Xray
    So that I may run the tests with a Test Automation Framework

    # Rules:
    #
    # 1) Feature files should be named <feature number>.feature
    # 2) Feature files should be written in <features dir>/ACTIVE/<feature file name>

    Scenario: Save downloaded feature files in an existing directory

        Given The feature files base directory is 'tmp/cucumber/downloaded-features'
        And   Directory 'tmp/cucumber/downloaded-features' has been created
        And   Xray Connector has retrieved feature files from Xray as a zipfile
        When  Xray Connector writes down feature files present in zipfile
        Then  File 'tmp/cucumber/downloaded-features/ACTIVE/1.feature' should exist
        